TEXT.S: kawas tay 1970, ryax sa tay 27 nqu tay 6, Ahmed Ahmed, squliq na Bunge'. qyanux na sraral Ahmed Ahmed byagan na ryax maki Helwan, Egypt. htgan qutux byacing lga musa maki Amirika la. mqyanux beh Riverside, California. mintzyuwaw nya Ahmed Ahmed hiya ga m' engi. t'aring sa kawas 1989, mtzyuwaw zyuwaw na engi ru mqwas. mincyogun nya mopu qeru kawas nya lga wal maki Hollywood. bincwagan mhtuw beh telibi. cyux si kaki kya mtzyaw.
